          "text": {
            "content": "Julian and I go out to fly my kite (Marcel) that I have yet to unleash into the sky this trip. We come back to and Julie (I’ve renamed Julian) makes me a truly delicious pasta. Filen makes a pretty incredible roti wrap and really enjoys the Marcel B. set that I request Julian to play again. ",
